CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FThe man accused of the murder of two
OL,7,Fmen on his land in Cornwall last year
OL,8,Fhas told his trial that one of his
OL,9,Falleged victims Daniel Coleman,
OL,10,Fdisposed of the body of the other
OL,11,Falleged victim Claudio Aquilino.
OL,13,FJames Desborough told the jury in his
OL,14,Ftrial he and Daniel Coleman had come
OL,15,Fback to woods at Sticker and found
OL,16,FClaudio Aquilino hanging from a tree.
OL,18,FMr Desborough said :"It was apparent
OL,19,FClaudio was gone. He wasn't alive. I
OL,20,Fflicked the slip knot on the side of
OL,21,Fthe tree he came onto the ground.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,F"There was a moment where, I was high,
OL,7,FI was on Ketamine at the time. Dan
OL,8,Fcame down, saw what was going on. Dan
OL,9,Fchecked feeling his pulse. There was
OL,10,Fno pulse. I was panicking.
OL,12,F"I had quite a lot of category A drugs
OL,13,Fon me and cannabis plants. "
OL,15,FMr Desborough told the jury Daniel
OL,16,FColeman had convinced him to carry on
OL,17,Fusing Claudio Aquilino's bank card and
OL,18,Fsaid it was Dan who got rid of Claudio
OL,19,FAquilino's body while he, Mr
OL,20,FDesborough, had disposed of his
OL,21,Fremains in the stream.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FHe said: "I sort of felt uneasy, I
OL,7,Ffelt pressured into it."
OL,9,FMr Desborough told the court he had
OL,10,Fbeen good friends with both Dan
OL,11,FColeman and Claudio Aquilino. He said
OL,12,Fhe had been living at the land in
OL,13,FSticker with both of them, but not at
OL,14,Fthe same time.
OL,16,FHe told the jury Daniel Coleman had
OL,17,Fcome back to the woods without his
OL,18,Fformer wife Hannah Cresswell and had
OL,19,Fbeen in a bad way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FMr Desborough said he had gone away
OL,7,Ffrom the woods himself in June last
OL,8,Fyear and when he came back he found
OL,9,FDaniel Coleman, naked and face down in
OL,10,Fthe stream dead.
OL,12,FHe told the jury he had lost all
OL,13,Fconcept of reality.
OL,15,FAsked what he decided to do with the
OL,16,Fbody he replied: "I cannot remember
OL,17,Fmaking any decision about dismembering
OL,18,FDan."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FAsked if he accepted that he did, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "I do - yes but I had drunk a
OL,8,Flot of tequila."
OL,10,FMr Desborough was asked repeatedly by
OL,11,Fhis defence Barrister Sean Brunton KC
OL,12,Fwhether he had killed Daniel Coleman
OL,13,Fand Claudio Aquilino. He repeatedly
OL,14,Freplied "No I didn't."
OL,16,FEarlier a pathologist told the jury
OL,17,Fthere was no conclusive cause of death
OL,18,Ffor Daniel Coleman.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FForensic pathologist Dr Amanda Jeffery
OL,7,Ftold Winchester Crown Court that the
OL,8,Fremains of Daniel Coleman were too
OL,9,Fbadly decomposed for her to reach any
OL,10,Fconclusion.
OL,12,FAsked by the defence whether he could
OL,13,Fhave died of natural causes, she said
OL,14,Fshe could not rule it out.
OL,16,FAsked by the prosecution if it was a
OL,17,Fcoincidence that two of James
OL,18,FDesborough's friends had both died on
OL,19,Fhis land weeks apart, Mr Desborough
OL,20,Freplied: "It was a series of
OL,21,Funfortunate circumstances."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FHe said he didn't remember a decision
OL,7,Fto dismember Daniel after he found his
OL,8,Fbody lying face down in the stream.
OL,10,FHe said: "I cannot remember thinking
OL,11,For making a decision to cut Dan up but
OL,12,FI admit that I did it."
OL,14,FAsked why he had never told the police
OL,15,For anyone else about what had happened
OL,16,Fon his land he said he wasn't thinking
OL,17,Fstraight at the time, saying he was
OL,18,Fdrinking and taking a variety of drugs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FProsecutor Ahmed Hossain KC suggested
OL,7,Fto Mr Desborough that he was the sort
OL,8,Fof man who could switch to violence
OL,9,Fand to kill very quickly.
OL,11,FMr Desborough admitted he had been
OL,12,Fconvicted of murdering his cell mate
OL,13,Fat Exeter Prison.
OL,15,F"You strangled your cell mate to death
OL,16,Fbecause he snored didn't you? he asked.
OL,18,F"No," replied Desborough.
OL,20,F"He irritated you by snoring so you
OL,21,Fstrangled him?" Hossain persisted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,F"No." replied Desborough.
OL,8,FMr Hossain asked Desborough if he got
OL,9,Fa thrill out of killing three people.
OL,10,FHe replied: "I did not kill three
OL,11,Fpeople. Exeter was an out of character
OL,12,Foffence."
OL,14,FThe prosecution asked James Desborough
OL,15,Fif he had killed both Claudio Aquilino
OL,16,Fand Daniel Coleman for their money.
OL,18,FDesborough admitted he had stolen from
OL,19,Fthem, using their bank cards after
OL,20,Fthey had died but repeated: "I didn't
OL,21,Fkill anybody."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784821695
OL,3,CMan accused of murdering two men in
OL,4,CCornwall gives evidence for first time
OL,6,FDesborough repeatedly said that he
OL,7,Fhadn't dismembered Claudio Aquilino's
OL,8,Fbody but admitted that he had cut
OL,9,FDaniel Coleman up with an axe.
OL,11,FHe said that Claudio's body had been
OL,12,Fkept in a caravan which was burnt to
OL,13,Fthe ground by Daniel Coleman.
OL,15,FHe said he had put Claudio's ashes in
OL,16,Fthe stream where everyone who lived on
OL,17,Fthe site used to wash using a metal
OL,18,Fbucket.
OL,20,FJames Desborough denies the murder of
OL,21,FDaniel Coleman and Claudio Aquilino.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
